data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own a slice of paradise. This 2020, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is situated on 1.57 private acres & is move in ready! Bedrooms have a walk-in closets & bathrooms have walk-in showers. The open kitchen features subway tile backsplash, stainless steel farmhouse sink, double oven & breakfast bar w/reverse osmosis filter. Stay comfortable year-round with electric forced air heat and cooling. Starlink equipment included for fast, reliable internet in the mountains! The laundry room has access to the covered back patio/garden. 9 raised garden beds, placed on $1000 of sand base, framed by a berm of lavender, irises & hydrangeas. An undeveloped year-round spring is on site and available for landscaping.  Enjoy Raspberries, blackberries, cherry tree, mint & herbs! Take in the views & watch wildlife from the covered front & back porches or stargaze by the graveled fire pit/picnic area! Also includes a gated entry, recycled asphalt driveway, woodshed, RV parking (no hook ups), French drain.
